{"word":"G3777 - οὔτε - oúte - oo'-teh - Neither","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οὔτε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">oúte</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">oo'-teh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Neither</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆவது, ஆகிலும் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"neither: and not"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3756 - οὐ - ou - oo/3756\">G3756</a> and <a href=\"#/G5037 - τέ - té - teh/5037\">G5037</a>; <i>not too</i>, that is, <i>neither</i> or <i>nor</i>; by analogy <i>not even:</i> - neither, none, nor (yet), (no, yet) not, nothing.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}